Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray an 8-inch square baking dish with vegetable cooking spray. Set aside. Make Filling: whisk together SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, cinnamon, orange zest and orange juice in a large bowl; add apples and toss to coat. Transfer mixture to prepared pan; set aside. Make Topping: stir together oats, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and cinnamon in a medium bowl; cut butter in with a pastry blender or 2 knives until mixture is crumbly. Stir in cereal and walnuts. Spoon topping over apples. Bake 45 minutes or until topping is lightly browned. Serve warm.